#Christkind on board! 👼
Today’s flight OS757 to Sarajevo took off with a special cargo: defence minister Klaudia Tanner handed over the first Advent wreaths to be transported to the Austrian soldiers of the @euforbih mission in #BosniaHerzegovina. 🕯️
